    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/cd0a25a34bcbeb1387d02b556d6e55e1.avif?t=1770840275\" width=600 height=129 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/e406c7b690e9950ae167b46be1e45def.avif?t=1770840275\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场意外的穿越，让你从慵懒的小猫化身为异世界的大猫贤者。眼前是流光溢彩的奥术洪流与危机四伏的奇幻大陆，从会说话的蘑菇到能喷吐烈焰的生物，一切都在考验你的智慧与勇气。你不再是旁观者，而是这片世界的冒险者与书写者。每一次前行都藏着未知，每一声咒语都可能点亮全新的奇迹喵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/f4a245b56a1cb0cf4762cb3f80872892.poster.avif?t=1770840275\" width=840 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/f4a245b56a1cb0cf4762cb3f80872892.webm?t=1770840275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/b10520e9d41b3766870f380372df9324.avif?t=1770840275\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里没有固定的招式，每一枚符文都是你创作的音符。火焰、冰霜、护盾与跳跃，随心组合便能编织出独一无二的奇迹。借助咒语引擎，你能创造任何想象得到的魔法，全程满是惊喜。当你举起爪子吟唱符文时，你的世界与战场将随之焕然一新喵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/884de6ebe6fc4d54fef2a137abdf60ec.poster.avif?t=1770840275\" width=850 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/884de6ebe6fc4d54fef2a137abdf60ec.webm?t=1770840275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/891d262c03ef5d6e3b180fd17e665ab8.avif?t=1770840275\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心创造的法术，不仅是力量，也是风险。敌人会偷学你的招式，用你最自豪的魔法来反击你。这里没有一招鲜的捷径，只有不断进化的思维与应变。唯有在混沌中保持冷静的猫法师，才能在危机中逆转乾坤，笑到最后喵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/776406774a3429ac40a725ac35fc996d.poster.avif?t=1770840275\" width=840 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/776406774a3429ac40a725ac35fc996d.webm?t=1770840275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/7455a80f89ec7a5eeaf02a2b3536adef.avif?t=1770840275\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里拥有几乎无限的法术组合，每一种新奇的搭配都是前所未有的创作。更重要的是，每一个被首次创造出来的法术，都会永久刻上创造者的名字，铭记于“万法之典”。你的智慧将化为不灭的传说，而你的名字会与奇迹一同流传！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/a4d48a0070e324d4b602cbc3e869ee86.poster.avif?t=1770840275\" width=850 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/a4d48a0070e324d4b602cbc3e869ee86.webm?t=1770840275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/eeb56223742b751e1e262fb314018d1e.avif?t=1770840275\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传送门已然开启，你的爪子虽小，却承载着改写世界规则的力量。这里没有攻略，只有你永不枯竭的智慧、勇气与创造力。踏入这片未知之地，你的冒险，将亲手谱写属于自己的奥术史诗喵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/eaaa6f36b177ecc2b0759e06635fd5a5.poster.avif?t=1770840275\" width=1170 height=650 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/eaaa6f36b177ecc2b0759e06635fd5a5.webm?t=1770840275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场关于选择与创造的旅程，属于你的篇章，正等待被点亮喵！<br><strong>其乐ID</strong>：1706296</p>",
